{"TopicId":191057,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to record on KSP?","CreatedByName":"qqmin","CreatedById":202339,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-17T10:52:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"qqmin","CreatedById":202339,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-17T10:52:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to record on KSP. Do you know any easy to use screen recorder? Paid or free is availble.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-01-17T10:54:01Z\u0022 title=\u002201/17/2020 10:54  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 17, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by qqmin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-17T10:58:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202339-qqmin/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022202339\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202339-qqmin/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@qqmin\u003C/a\u003E, I use a free program called \u003Ca href=\u0022https://obsproject.com/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EOpen Broadcaster Software\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(OBS). This \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSiYpluD0fY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E5 minute video\u003C/a\u003E explains basic setup - I found it very easy to use.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RizzoTheRat","CreatedById":123362,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-17T11:19:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re using Windows 10 there\u0027s a built in recorder, Win-G to bring up the Game Bar that contains the record button, or Win-Alt-R to record without bringing up the toolbar.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWindows built in Photo app will let you do really basic editing like trimming or overlaying some text or adding music, but if you\u0027re uploading to the internet be very careful with music as you get it blocked due to rights ownership.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-18T10:01:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223729195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191057\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221579258701\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202339-qqmin/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022202339\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/202339-qqmin/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@qqmin\u003C/a\u003E, I use a free program called \u003Ca href=\u0022https://obsproject.com/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EOpen Broadcaster Software\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(OBS). This \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dSiYpluD0fY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E5 minute video\u003C/a\u003E explains basic setup - I found it very easy to use.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI second this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-01-18T11:24:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=